




{"id":16468,"date":"2025-07-01T13:49:42","date_gmt":"2025-07-01T06:49:42","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/?p=16468"},"modified":"2025-07-01T16:21:27","modified_gmt":"2025-07-01T09:21:27","slug":"5-ly-do-nen-chon-man-hinh-tuong-tac-thay-vi-khung-tuong-tac-cho-lop-hoc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/5-ly-do-nen-chon-man-hinh-tuong-tac-thay-vi-khung-tuong-tac-cho-lop-hoc\/","title":{"rendered":"5 L\u00fd Do N\u00ean Ch\u1ecdn M\u00e0n H\u00ecnh T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Thay V\u00ec Khung T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Cho L\u1edbp H\u1ecdc"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_78 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">N\u1ed9i dung ch\u00ednh<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/5-ly-do-nen-chon-man-hinh-tuong-tac-thay-vi-khung-tuong-tac-cho-lop-hoc\/#duoi_day_la_5_ly_do_khien_khien_cac_co_so_giao_duc_nen_uu_tien_lua_chon_man_hinh_tuong_tac_thay_vi_khung_tuong_tac\" >D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c n\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c thay v\u00ec khung t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c:<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/5-ly-do-nen-chon-man-hinh-tuong-tac-thay-vi-khung-tuong-tac-cho-lop-hoc\/#bang_so_sanh_chi_tiet_man_hinh_tuong_tac_voi_khung_tuong_tac\" >B\u1ea3ng so s\u00e1nh chi ti\u1ebft: M\u00e0n H\u00ecnh T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c v\u1edbi Khung T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/5-ly-do-nen-chon-man-hinh-tuong-tac-thay-vi-khung-tuong-tac-cho-lop-hoc\/#vi_sao_nen_chon_innosmart\" >V\u00ec sao n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn INNOSMART?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong xu th\u1ebf chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 ng\u00e0nh gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c, vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y th\u00f4ng minh ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng. Nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc gi\u1eefa m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 khung t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c \u0111ang d\u1ea7n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u1ebf l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-16471 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Man-hinh-tuong-tac-cho-giao-duc.webp\" alt=\"5 L\u00fd Do N\u00ean Ch\u1ecdn M\u00e0n H\u00ecnh T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Thay V\u00ec Khung T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Cho L\u1edbp H\u1ecdc\" width=\"900\" height=\"594\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Man-hinh-tuong-tac-cho-giao-duc.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Man-hinh-tuong-tac-cho-giao-duc-606x400.webp 606w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Man-hinh-tuong-tac-cho-giao-duc-768x507.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Man-hinh-tuong-tac-cho-giao-duc-600x396.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"duoi_day_la_5_ly_do_khien_khien_cac_co_so_giao_duc_nen_uu_tien_lua_chon_man_hinh_tuong_tac_thay_vi_khung_tuong_tac\"><\/span><strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c n\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c thay v\u00ec khung t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><b>Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ngo\u00e0i, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c l\u00e0 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb t\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1eb5n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3: m\u00e0n hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb, h\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh, ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, loa v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, khung t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb b\u1ed5 tr\u1ee3, c\u1ea7n k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u1ea3ng, m\u00e1y t\u00ednh, c\u00e1p t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u, v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i hi\u1ec7u ch\u1ec9nh th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ti\u1ec7n trong v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 ph\u00e1t sinh l\u1ed7i k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-16473 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/z6757619183004_2959f8d373d15e889bf04c8de3424cf2.webp\" alt=\"5 L\u00fd Do N\u00ean Ch\u1ecdn M\u00e0n H\u00ecnh T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Thay V\u00ec Khung T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Cho L\u1edbp H\u1ecdc\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/z6757619183004_2959f8d373d15e889bf04c8de3424cf2.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/z6757619183004_2959f8d373d15e889bf04c8de3424cf2-711x400.webp 711w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/z6757619183004_2959f8d373d15e889bf04c8de3424cf2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/z6757619183004_2959f8d373d15e889bf04c8de3424cf2-600x337.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><b>Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c mang l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh s\u1eafc n\u00e9t, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb l\u1ec7ch ho\u1eb7c nh\u00f2e. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u ch\u1ec9nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1m hay c\u0103n g\u00f3c nh\u01b0 khi d\u00f9ng khung t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c. Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u00f2n c\u00f3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u00f3a v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u1eaft cho h\u1ecdc sinh v\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-16470 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/z6757567931603_f4ee38a7520135f729787f82ba00e46b.webp\" alt=\"5 L\u00fd Do N\u00ean Ch\u1ecdn M\u00e0n H\u00ecnh T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Thay V\u00ec Khung T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Cho L\u1edbp H\u1ecdc\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/z6757567931603_f4ee38a7520135f729787f82ba00e46b.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/z6757567931603_f4ee38a7520135f729787f82ba00e46b-711x400.webp 711w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/z6757567931603_f4ee38a7520135f729787f82ba00e46b-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/z6757567931603_f4ee38a7520135f729787f82ba00e46b-600x337.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><b>T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u00f3m<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00f9ng l\u00fac nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea1m, cho ph\u00e9p nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ecdc sinh thao t\u00e1c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng l\u00fac. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u1eefu \u00edch trong c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u00f3m, gi\u1ea3i b\u00e0i t\u1eadp chung ho\u1eb7c tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y. Khung t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-16472 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/man-hinh-tuong-tac-thong-minh-lop-hoc-1.webp\" alt=\"5 L\u00fd Do N\u00ean Ch\u1ecdn M\u00e0n H\u00ecnh T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Thay V\u00ec Khung T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Cho L\u1edbp H\u1ecdc\" width=\"900\" height=\"612\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/man-hinh-tuong-tac-thong-minh-lop-hoc-1.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/man-hinh-tuong-tac-thong-minh-lop-hoc-1-588x400.webp 588w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/man-hinh-tuong-tac-thong-minh-lop-hoc-1-768x522.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/man-hinh-tuong-tac-thong-minh-lop-hoc-1-600x408.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><b>T\u0103ng t\u00ednh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho ph\u00e9p t\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111a d\u1ea1ng n\u1ed9i dung: video, c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 t\u01b0 duy, tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp&#8230; gi\u00fap b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n. H\u1ecdc sinh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u201cnghe \u2013 ghi ch\u00e9p\u201d b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 khung t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c \u2013 v\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ghi ch\u00fa \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u2013 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-16474 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/ttang-su-tuong-tac-12-1.webp\" alt=\"5 L\u00fd Do N\u00ean Ch\u1ecdn M\u00e0n H\u00ecnh T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Thay V\u00ec Khung T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c Cho L\u1edbp H\u1ecdc\" width=\"900\" height=\"510\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/ttang-su-tuong-tac-12-1.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/ttang-su-tuong-tac-12-1-706x400.webp 706w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/ttang-su-tuong-tac-12-1-768x435.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/ttang-su-tuong-tac-12-1-600x340.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><b>\u0110\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n \u2013 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, \u00edt b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 khung t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3, d\u1ec5 l\u1ed7i c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng ho\u1eb7c l\u1ec7ch khung, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9 v\u00e0 \u00edt c\u1ea7n b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, k\u00ednh c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea7y x\u01b0\u1edbc, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u2013 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 gi\u00fap ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bang_so_sanh_chi_tiet_man_hinh_tuong_tac_voi_khung_tuong_tac\"><\/span><strong>B\u1ea3ng so s\u00e1nh chi ti\u1ebft: M\u00e0n H\u00ecnh T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c v\u1edbi Khung T\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00e1c\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<table style=\"width: 93.2746%;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 18.4579%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><b>Ti\u00eau ch\u00ed<\/b><\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 41.9782%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><b>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c<\/b><\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 38.8629%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><b>Khung t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c<\/b><\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 18.4579%;\"><b>T\u00ednh t\u00edch h\u1ee3p<\/b><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 41.9782%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 trong m\u1ed9t: m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh + c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng + h\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh + loa + ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 38.8629%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ph\u1ee5, c\u1ea7n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p m\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu + b\u1ea3ng tr\u1eafng + m\u00e1y t\u00ednh<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 18.4579%;\"><b>Hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb<\/b><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 41.9782%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh s\u1eafc n\u00e9t, ch\u1ed1ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh, kh\u00f4ng m\u1ecfi m\u1eaft<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 38.8629%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o TV, m\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu: d\u1ec5 m\u1edd, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 18.4579%;\"><b>T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng<\/b><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 41.9782%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m, m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 38.8629%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u ch\u1ec9nh th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng, d\u1ec5 l\u1ec7ch v\u1ecb tr\u00ed<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 18.4579%;\"><b>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf &amp; l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t<\/b><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 41.9782%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1eafm \u0111i\u1ec7n l\u00e0 d\u00f9ng<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 38.8629%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p, c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u ch\u1ec9nh, c\u0103n khung, ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1ea3ng\/m\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 18.4579%;\"><b>T\u00ednh linh ho\u1ea1t khi d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc<\/b><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 41.9782%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp + tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, chia nh\u00f3m, ghi ch\u00fa, ph\u00e1t video, tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu, v\u1ebd s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 38.8629%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 thao t\u00e1c vi\u1ebft\/v\u1ebd \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 18.4579%;\"><b>B\u1ea3o tr\u00ec &amp; tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd<\/b><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 41.9782%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00cdt b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n c\u0103n ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3, tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd cao<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 38.8629%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u1ec5 l\u1ec7ch khung, c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u ch\u1ec9nh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, d\u1ec5 h\u01b0 h\u1ecfng c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 18.4579%;\"><b>Chi ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ban \u0111\u1ea7u<\/b><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 41.9782%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cao h\u01a1n<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 38.8629%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 18.4579%;\"><b>Chi ph\u00ed d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n (b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec, v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh)<\/b><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 41.9782%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">R\u1ebb h\u01a1n do b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9, ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111i\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n m\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu<\/span><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 38.8629%;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ed1n th\u00eam chi ph\u00ed cho thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ph\u1ee5, thay th\u1ebf TV, m\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu, c\u0103n ch\u1ec9nh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb v\u1eeba tr\u1ef1c quan, d\u1ec5 d\u00f9ng, v\u1eeba h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf m\u1ecdi c\u1ea5p h\u1ecdc \u2013 th\u00ec m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c INNOSMART ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"vi_sao_nen_chon_innosmart\"><\/span><b>V\u00ec sao n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn<\/b> <b>INNOSMART?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c , t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c linh ho\u1ea1t, ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng cho m\u1ecdi thao t\u00e1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4K si\u00eau s\u1eafc n\u00e9t, t\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ch\u1ed1ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u1eaft<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 ti\u1ec7n \u00edch: truy\u1ec1n t\u1ec7p, b\u1ecf phi\u1ebfu, ghi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh, h\u1eb9n gi\u1edd, ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc, h\u1ecdp.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Android 14.0 <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">v\u1edbi b\u1ea3ng tr\u1eafng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed t\u00edch h\u1ee3p<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> d\u1ec5 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 chia s\u1ebb m\u00e3 QR, ch\u00fa th\u00edch nhanh v\u00e0 chia s\u1ebb n\u1ed9i dung hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chia s\u1ebb m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb (m\u00e1y t\u00ednh, \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i) v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c ngay tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i \u0111a d\u1ea1ng <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ngo\u1ea1i vi<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n cao, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trong xu th\u1ebf chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 ng\u00e0nh gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c, vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y th\u00f4ng minh ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng. Nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc gi\u1eefa m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 khung t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":16476,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-16468","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16468","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{